We know that the ratio
of let's say CB to BA,

00:07:09.024 --> 00:07:10.396
so let's write this down.

00:07:10.396 --> 00:07:13.421
We know that the ratio, so this tells us

00:07:13.421 --> 00:07:15.473
that the ratio of corresponding sides

00:07:15.473 --> 00:07:16.551
