00:07:16.551 --> 00:07:18.801
So, the ratio of CB over BA

00:07:22.823 --> 00:07:25.352
is going to be equal to...

00:07:25.352 --> 00:07:29.084
Well, the corresponding side to CB,

00:07:29.084 --> 00:07:31.639
it's the side opposite the X degree angle

00:07:31.639 --> 00:07:32.633
right over here.

00:07:32.633 --> 00:07:35.551
So, the corresponding
side to CB is side AD.

00:07:35.551 --> 00:07:38.884
So, that's going to be equal to AD over,

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:42.787
what's the corresponding side to BA?

00:07:42.787 --> 00:07:45.037
Well, BA is opposite the Y degree angle.

00:07:45.037 --> 00:07:47.562
So, over here the
corresponding side is DE.

00:07:47.562 --> 00:07:48.479
AD over DE.

00:07:50.105 --> 00:07:52.530
Let me do that same color.

00:07:52.530 --> 00:07:53.363
Over DE.

